We combine these objectives using scaling factors $\beta_C, \beta_{GME}, \beta_\tau,$ and $\beta_E$:
\begin{equation}
  \label{eq:outerobj}
  \mathrm{Obj}(x)=\beta_C C(x)+\beta_{GME} GME(x)+\beta_\tau \tau'(x)+\beta_E E(x).
\end{equation}

